title: George And Amal Clooney Are Expecting Twins | Letty B | 102 The River
text:
George And Amal Clooney Are Expecting Twins posted by Letty B - share 
Source: Getty 
AHHH, huge congrats to the Clooney family. Amal is pregnant and is expecting TWINS! Looks like Beyonce isn't the only star expecting two bundles of joy. 
TMZ revealed that Amal is pregnant with a boy and a girl. While other sources confirmed to Us Weekly that she has an early summer due date, most likely in June. How exciting for the Clooney fam!
